<br>
Would wizards want more bane spells tossed in the game? Hrm, that's a tough one. Would there be bane spells for all types of monster encountered, or just the common ones (Froglok, Gnoll, Orc etc.)?<br>
Would there be upgraded versions, or would those bane spells eventually end up in the back of our spellbooks?<br>
Would the lower level bane spells use reagents like their big brothers do?<br>
